summary: Sansa sat up. "Lady," she whispered. For a moment it was as if the direwolf was there in the room, looking at her with those...
caption: Sansa sat up. “Lady,” she whispered. For a moment it was as if the direwolf was there in the room, looking at her with those golden eyes, sad and knowing. She had been dreaming, she realized. Lady was with her, and they were running together, and … and … trying to remember was like trying to catch the rain with her fingers. The dream faded, and Lady was dead again.

these are the three characters that expressed wishes in the first episode i think
correct me if any others did too
summary: sansa stark: wish expressed in first episode: to become queen suffering in first episode: has food thrown at her endgame:...
body:
sansa stark:

wish expressed in first episode: to become queen

suffering in first episode: has food thrown at her

endgame: becomes a queen

jon snow:

wish expressed in first episode: to join the nights watch

suffering in first episode: receives a cold look from his step-mother, prohibited from attending a feast

endgame: abandons the nights watch to go live with the free folk

daenerys targaryen:

wish expressed in first episode: to go home

suffering in first episode: sexually assaulted and emotionally abused by her brother, threatened with gang rape, sold into glorified sexual slavery, raped

endgame: murdered just as she reaches her home

so of the three characters that expressed a wish in the first episode, the one that gets villainised and killed off is the one who had the most basic wish and endured extreme suffering since day one

*Gendry burst through the door*

Sansa:…

Sansa, whispering: She’s talking shit… she’s getting hit

summary: “Welcoming Winter” ~ Sansan kissy in the snow... XD  I am in DEEEEEP right now with this ship I cannot even handle myself....
caption:
“Welcoming Winter” ~ Sansan kissy in the snow… XD

I am in DEEEEEP right now with this ship I cannot even handle myself. Wanted this out of my system desperately before finishing my Sansan Secret Santa July thing… I’m almost done sketching that one out and will need to add color. 

I have a THING about drawing my ships in snow… ugh… I cannot stop drawing these two! I am really enjoying the Sansan community here on tumblr and all the great PRIMO fanfics out there! Send me recs people! I’ve read a lot, but I KNOW I haven’t read them all. I’m really enjoying modern day AU as well as alternate ending AU among others. Yay! XD
